  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0daf\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0dc4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb \u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dab \u0db4\u0dd2\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dd2 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dbb\u0dd4. \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u00a047\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dba\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "To catch grasshoppers to the land where the gate has been damaged Rs. 47 lakhs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Urban Development Authority, the damage done to the land that was established near the Galle mouth by the name of Gotagogama is about 49 lakh rupees.",
        "The authority also says that they have now taken steps to get an assessment report on the damage caused to the golf course.",
        "It is stated in the assessment report prepared by the Urban Development Authority that 1.5 lakh rupees will be spent for the resettlement and basic works of the land and 47.5 lakh rupees for the weed control.",
        "The minister in charge of the subject, Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga, had recently instructed the Urban Development Authority to take necessary legal measures to recover compensation from the activists for the damage caused to the area around the golf course belonging to the Urban Development Authority.",
        "For about 3 months, the group of protesters stayed in the area around the golf course without permission, asking former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa to resign from his position. After Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa left the office of the President, the court informed the activists to leave the place and accordingly they had to leave the place."
      ],
